
### **SysBackground.enableHcaptchaSolver(autoOpen)**

**Description:**
The `SysBackground.enableHcaptchaSolver(autoOpen)` function enables the automatic solving of hCaptcha challenges using the `SysContent.enableSafeHcaptchaSolver` method. The `autoOpen` parameter specifies whether the hCaptcha anchor should automatically open or not.

**Parameters:**
- **autoOpen** (Boolean): If set to `true`, the hCaptcha anchor will automatically open. If set to `false`, the anchor will not be opened automatically.

**Example:**

```javascript
SysBackground.enableHcaptchaSolver(true);  // Automatically open the hCaptcha anchor and start solving.
```